00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:04.365
The model component correspond to data related logic.

00:00:04.365 --> 00:00:08.519
Model can be represented as data being transferred between

00:00:08.519 --> 00:00:13.544
the view and the controller or other logic related data.

00:00:13.544 --> 00:00:20.550
If we are creating a student management application to store students' grade,

00:00:20.550 --> 00:00:27.045
we can create a student object to retrieve the student records from the database,

00:00:27.045 --> 00:00:29.910
process it and update the database,

00:00:29.910 --> 00:00:32.534
is updated student record,

00:00:32.534 --> 00:00:36.549
or pass it to the view to render it.

